# Master distillation pipeline — keep run state, LLM logs, and curated
# outputs in the repo (the audit trail is reproducible). The full raw
# transcript IS the book end-to-end and stays out of a public repo for
# copyright; everything else under runs/ commits cleanly.
pipelines/master-distillation/runs/*/raw-transcript.txt
